  <h1>From Gold to Code</h1>
  <p><strong>Subtitle:</strong> Evolution of Money to CBDCs</p>
  <p><strong>BLUF:</strong> CBDCs convert money from a bearer asset and accounting entry into a programmable policy instrument directly controlled by the central bank. You gain instant settlement and precise policy delivery; you lose transactional privacy and introduce governance risk.</p>

